Returns a list of previously analysed [private files](https://gtidocs.virustotal.com/reference/private-files-object). The files are always ordered by SHA256.

```json /api/v3/private/files
{
  "meta": {
    "cursor": <string>,
    "count": <int>
  },
  "data": {
